      </style></div><div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center lg:mt-28 mb-12"><div class="flex justify-center md:justify-start"><img src="/car-images/kia-hero.jpg" alt="Used Kia auto parts hero image" class="w-full max-w-md rounded-2xl shadow-xl"/></div><div class="flex flex-col justify-center"><h3 class="font-semibold text-xl md:text-2xl mb-3 text-white">Used Kia Auto Parts for Sale</h3><p class="text-[18px] leading-[30px] text-[#cecece]">Smart. Affordable. Reliable. That’s PartsCentral. Kia owners love the perfect mix of innovation, reliability, and affordability. At PartsCentral, we help you preserve that value with OEM used Kia auto parts that are tested, trusted, and shipped nationwide. From compact hatchbacks to spacious SUVs, we’ve got your Kia covered without breaking the budget.</p></div></div><div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-14"><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Smart. Affordable. Reliable. That’s PartsCentral.</h3><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-[#cecece]"><li>OEM used Kia auto parts tested and trusted</li><li>Nationwide shipping across the United States</li><li>Affordable solutions without sacrificing quality</li><li>Designed to keep Kia vehicles running reliably</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Built for Drivers Who Think Smart</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">Kia drivers expect tech-forward features, solid performance, and a ride that fits their lifestyle — all without overspending. That’s where our used auto parts for Kia come in: OEM fit, quality-assured, and priced right to keep you moving forward confidently.</p></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Kia Auto Parts We Carry</h3><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-[#cecece]"><li>Engines, transmissions, cooling systems</li><li>Radiators, fans, AC compressors</li><li>Window regulators and motors</li><li>Starters, alternators, electrical parts</li><li>Doors, fenders, mirrors, bumpers</li><li>Suspension, axles, control arms</li><li>Headlights, taillights, switches</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Quality You Can Count On</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">Every used Kia auto part we ship goes through rigorous inspection by our in-house experts. We check for performance, safety, and fit, and we don’t list it unless it passes. No shortcuts. No surprises. Just ready-to-install parts.</p></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Skip the Dealer Price Tag</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">Why pay full price when OEM auto parts for Kia deliver the same performance for less? Get a fast, free quote from PartsCentral — no login, no pressure. We respond quickly and ship even faster.</p></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Kia Models We Support</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">We cover nearly every Kia model. Need something rare or older? We’ll help track it down through our extended Kia auto parts store network.</p><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-1 text-[#cecece]"><li>Kia Cadenza</li><li>Kia Forte</li><li>Kia K5</li><li>Kia Niro</li><li>Kia Optima</li><li>Kia Rio</li><li>Kia Rondo</li><li>Kia Seltos</li><li>Kia Sorento</li><li>Kia Soul</li><li>Kia Spectra</li><li>Kia Sportage</li><li>Kia Stinger</li><li>Kia Telluride</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Why Kia Drivers Choose PartsCentral</h3><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-[#cecece]"><li>Rigorous quality inspections</li><li>Nationwide shipping</li><li>Competitive pricing</li><li>Secure checkout and easy returns</li><li>Prompt customer support available 7 days a week</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Get Your Kia Back on the Road</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">Whether you search Kia auto parts near me or want to order Kia auto parts online, PartsCentral makes it simple. Search your model, request a quote, and place your order in minutes. Join thousands of Kia owners who trust PartsCentral for affordable, high-quality used Kia auto parts that just work.</p><p class="mt-4 font-bold text-white">Request a free quote today.</p></div></div><div class="w-full mt-20 py-16 sm:py-20 px-4 sm:px-8  bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 text-center rounded-2xl"><h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Find Quality <!-- -->Used Kia Auto Parts for Sale<!-- --> Parts Today?</h2><p class="text-white/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8 text-sm sm:text-base">Get fast pricing, expert guidance, and nationwide delivery on quality used auto parts for your <!-- -->Used Kia Auto Parts for Sale<!-- -->.</p><a href="/" class="inline-block  bg-[#00A3FF]  text-white px-7 sm:px-9 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,163,255,0.45)] hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(0,163,255,0.7)] transition-all duration-300 hover:opacity-95">Find My Parts</a></div></section><section class="w-full flex flex-col items-center px-6 py-16 bg-[#07142B] text-[#E8F3FF]"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-orbitron mb-10 text-center">USED <!-- -->KIA<!-- --> AUTO PARTS</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto"><ul class="space-y-2 text-lg leading-7 font-jaldi list-disc list-inside text-[#cecece]"><li>Kia<!-- --> <!-- -->Engine Assembly</li><li>Kia<!-- --> <!-- -->Transmission</li><li>Kia<!-- --> <!-- -->ABS Control Module</li><li>Kia<!-- --> <!-- -->ABS System (Anti-Lock)</li><li>Kia<!-- --> <!-- -->AC Compressor</li><li>Kia<!-- --> <!-- -->AC Compressor Clutch</li><li>Kia<!-- --> <!-- -->AC Condenser</li><li>Kia<!-- --> <!-- -->AC Evaporator</li><li>Kia<!-- --> <!-- -->Air Bag